Prohibited items include metal cutlery and other sharp items, drink bottles and unsealed lids (including bottles of water or soft drink), scooters, bikes, pets, glass, marquees and any large portable structures.

South Bank Parklands will be an alcohol-free site on the day. Alcohol consumption is only permitted within licensed restaurant or bar venues. 

Public transport is the best mode of transport. Use Translinks website to plan ahead. Free travel will be available on Translink buses, trains and ferries from 8pm on 31 December 2024 to 5:30am on 1 January 2025.

Works will impact the Beenleigh and Gold Coast train lines over this period. Visit Cross River Rails website for information.

The Gold Coast New Years Eve Cruise is the perfect way to ring in 2025! Sail along the Gold Coast waterways and enjoy the fireworks aboard the Spirit of Elston. 

The cruise begins along the canals, taking in the stunning Surfers Paradise skyline, before heading out to the Gold Coast Broadwater for the City of Gold Coast midnight fireworks from open-top decks. 

Enjoy a glass of Chandon on arrival along with gourmet canaps and a great selection of beverages including local wines, premium beers, and cider throughout the evening.

La crociera di Capodanno della Gold Coast  il modo perfetto per festeggiare il 2025! Naviga lungo i corsi d'acqua della Gold Coast e goditi i fuochi d'artificio a bordo dello Spirit of Elston. 

La crociera inizia lungo i canali, ammirando lo splendido skyline di Surfers Paradise, prima di dirigersi verso Gold Coast Broadwater per i fuochi d'artificio di mezzanotte della citt di Gold Coast dai ponti scoperti. 

Goditi un bicchiere di Chandon all'arrivo insieme a tartine gourmet e un'ottima selezione di bevande tra cui vini locali, birre premium e sidro per tutta la serata.

La croisire du rveillon du Nouvel An sur la Gold Coast est le moyen idal pour clbrer 2025! Naviguez le long des voies navigables de la Gold Coast et profitez des feux d'artifice  bord du Spirit of Elston. 

La croisire commence le long des canaux, en admirant la magnifique ligne d'horizon de Surfers Paradise, avant de se diriger vers la Gold Coast Broadwater pour les feux d'artifice de minuit de la ville de Gold Coast depuis les ponts ouverts. 

Profitez d'un verre de Chandon  votre arrive accompagn de canaps gastronomiques et d'une grande slection de boissons, notamment des vins locaux, des bires haut de gamme et du cidre tout au long de la soire.

O Cruzeiro de Ano Novo em Gold Coast  a maneira perfeita de comemorar 2025! Navegue pelos canais de Gold Coast e curta os fogos de artifcio a bordo do Spirit of Elston. 

O cruzeiro comea ao longo dos canais, contemplando o deslumbrante horizonte de Surfers Paradise, antes de seguir para Gold Coast Broadwater para os fogos de artifcio da meia-noite da cidade de Gold Coast em decks abertos. 

Desfrute de uma taa de Chandon na chegada, juntamente com canaps gourmet e uma grande seleo de bebidas, incluindo vinhos locais, cervejas premium e cidra durante toda a noite.

2025

Pelayaran Malam Tahun Baru Gold Coast adalah cara sempurna untuk merayakan tahun 2025! Berlayar di sepanjang perairan Gold Coast dan nikmati kembang api di atas kapal Spirit of Elston. 

Pelayaran dimulai di sepanjang kanal, menikmati cakrawala Surfers Paradise yang menakjubkan, sebelum menuju ke Gold Coast Broadwater untuk menyaksikan pertunjukan kembang api tengah malam Kota Gold Coast dari dek terbuka. 

Nikmati segelas Chandon pada saat kedatangan bersama dengan makanan kecil gourmet dan berbagai pilihan minuman termasuk anggur lokal, bir premium, dan sari buah apel sepanjang malam.

Die Silvesterkreuzfahrt an der Gold Coast ist die perfekte Art, das Jahr 2025 einzuluten! Segeln Sie entlang der Wasserstraen der Gold Coast und genieen Sie das Feuerwerk an Bord der Spirit of Elston. 

Die Kreuzfahrt beginnt entlang der Kanle und bietet einen atemberaubenden Blick auf die Skyline von Surfers Paradise, bevor es zum Gold Coast Broadwater geht, wo Sie von offenen Decks aus das Mitternachtsfeuerwerk der Stadt Gold Coast erleben. 

Genieen Sie bei Ihrer Ankunft ein Glas Chandon sowie Gourmet-Canaps und eine groe Auswahl an Getrnken, darunter lokale Weine, Premium-Biere und Apfelwein den ganzen Abend ber.

El crucero de Nochevieja en Gold Coast es la manera perfecta de recibir el 2025! Navegue por los canales de Gold Coast y disfrute de los fuegos artificiales a bordo del Spirit of Elston. 

El crucero comienza a lo largo de los canales, contemplando el impresionante horizonte de Surfers Paradise, antes de dirigirse a Gold Coast Broadwater para ver los fuegos artificiales de medianoche de la ciudad de Gold Coast desde cubiertas abiertas. 

Disfrute de una copa de Chandon a su llegada junto con canaps gourmet y una gran seleccin de bebidas que incluyen vinos locales, cervezas premium y sidra durante toda la noche.
